			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "EMC Storage Starter. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Klein Star Zwei is an EMC storage item added by ProjectE. It holds up to 200,000 EMC and is also used in the crafting of Klein Star Drei. "
				""
				"It can be charged by being placed in a Transmutation Table and being feed in items, or by being placed in the charging slot of an Energy Collector or Anti-Matter Relay. Klein Stars are discharged by being placed in the discharging slot of an Anti-Matter Relay. If a charged Klein Star is placed in the \"flames\" slot of a Transmutation Table, the star will be destroyed, converted to EMC and any stored energy will be lost"
			]
			dependencies: ["5E2127A7705A4A6F"]
