			y: -3.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "EMC Transfer MK I. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Anti-Matter Relay MK1 is an EMC manipulator added by ProjectE."
				""
				"This machine serves two functions. Firstly, any item placed into its inventory will be converted into EMC. Secondly, it transfers energy from Energy Collectors to Energy Condensers. When transferring, it gives a small, 1 EMC per second bonus. It is also used to charge the Klein Star series with EMC.It can transfer up to 64 EMC/s and can store up to 100,000 EMC."
			]
